taxi.resource

Class RequestHandlingInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • taxi.resource.RequestHandlingInfo

  • public class RequestHandlingInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    The RequestHandlingInfo class implements the xml representation of a request, needed from RequestHandlingResource

    Every RequestHandlingInfo has:

    • reqId,
    • taxiId,
    • cost,
    • duration,
    • customerId,
    • decision,
    • fromAddress,
    • fromZipCode,
    • fromCity,
    • toAddress,
    • toZipCode,
    • toCity

    Since:
    Academic Year 2016-2017
    Author:
    Team 4
